\begin_layout Standard
四维坐标本身是矢量：
\begin_inset Formula $x^{\prime,\mu}=\Lambda_{\phantom{\mu}\nu}^{\mu}x^{\nu}$
\end_inset

，设
\begin_inset Formula $L$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $\Lambda$
\end_inset

的逆矩阵，
\begin_inset Formula $x^{\mu}={\color{blue}L_{\phantom{\mu}\nu}^{\mu}x^{\prime,\nu}}$
\end_inset

。
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\text{标量：}\quad & s\left(x^{\rho}\right)\rightarrow s\left({\color{blue}L_{\phantom{\mu}\sigma}^{\rho}x^{\prime\sigma}}\right)\\
\text{四维矢量：}\quad & V^{\mu}\left(x^{\rho}\right)\rightarrow\Lambda_{\phantom{\mu}\nu}^{\mu}V^{\nu}\left({\color{blue}L_{\phantom{\mu}\sigma}^{\rho}x^{\prime\sigma}}\right)\\
\text{四\text{维张量}：}\quad & T^{\mu\nu}\left(x^{\rho}\right)\to\Lambda_{\phantom{\mu}\alpha}^{\mu}\Lambda_{\phantom{\mu}\beta}^{\nu}T^{\alpha\beta}\left({\color{blue}L_{\phantom{\mu}\sigma}^{\rho}x^{\prime\sigma}}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

这样就将场的时空依赖转换到新坐标系下。注意场分量和坐标的变换矩阵不同，它们互逆。
