\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left[\begin{array}{c}
E_{1}/c\\
p_{1}
\end{array}\right]+\left[\begin{array}{c}
m_{2}c\\
0
\end{array}\right]=\left[\begin{array}{c}
E_{1}/c+m_{2}c\\
p_{1}
\end{array}\right]
\]

\end_inset

所以系统整体的速度是，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\beta c=c^{2}\frac{p_{1}}{E_{1}+m_{2}c^{2}}=\frac{c\sqrt{E_{1}^{2}-m_{1}^{2}c^{4}}}{E_{1}+m_{2}c^{2}}
\]

